'''伊利亚·阿列克謝耶維奇·朱托米尔斯基'''（{{lang-en|'''Ilya Alexeyevich Zhitomirskiy'''}}，{{lang-ru|'''Илья Алексеевич Житомирский'''}}，{{bd|1989年|10月12日|2011年|11月12日}}）<ref name="NYTObit">{{Cite news|title = Ilya Zhitomirskiy Dies at 22; Co-Founded Social Network|first = Paul|last = Vitello|date = 15 November 2011|accessdate = 2011-11-16|url = http://www.nytimes.com/2011/11/16/technology/ilya-zhitomirskiy-co-founder-of-social-network-dies-at-22.html|newspaper = [[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|archive-date = 2015-09-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150928235553/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/11/16/technology/ilya-zhitomirskiy-co-founder-of-social-network-dies-at-22.html}}</ref>是一位俄罗斯裔美国人，曾是[[软件设计师|软件设计师]]和创业者。朱托米尔斯基是 Diaspora社交网络的合作创始人和[[Diaspora_(软件)|Diaspora 软件]]的初始开发者之一，并是其主导者。

== 生平 ==

=== 早年生活 ===
朱托米尔斯基在1989年10月12日出生于[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]。其父亲为阿列克謝·密托維科夫（Alexei Medovikov），母亲为恩娜·朱托米爾斯卡雅（Inna Zhitomirskaya）。其父亲与其祖父均为数学家。2000年，朱托米尔斯基随其父移民美国，最后定居于[[费城|费城]]郊外，并在当地的{{tsl|en|Lower Merion High School|劳尔梅里恩高中}}学习至2007年毕业。他先前也在位于[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]的{{tsl|en|Acton|阿克顿镇}}的{{tsl|en|Acton-Boxborough Regional High School|阿克顿-巴克斯柏路地区高中}}学习。随后，他在[[杜兰大学|杜兰大学]]、[[马里兰大学学院市分校|马里兰大学学院市分校]]、[[纽约大学|纽约大学]]学习了数学、计算机科学和经济学。在其业余时间，朱托米尔斯基喜爱骑[[单轮车|单轮车]]并且是一名职业舞厅舞者。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/11/16/technology/ilya-zhitomirskiy-co-founder-of-social-network-dies-at-22.html |title=Paul Vitello (15 November 2011). |accessdate=2016-02-04 |archive-date=2015-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928235553/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/11/16/technology/ilya-zhitomirskiy-co-founder-of-social-network-dies-at-22.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 创建Diaspora ===
在纽约大学时，他在[[科朗数学研究所|科朗数学研究所]]学习计算机科学，并于2010年在那里遇见了与他共同创建[[Diaspora_(软件)|DIASPORA*]]的三个朋友<ref name="Gawker14Nov11">{{cite web |url=http://gawker.com/ilya-zhitomirskiy/ |title=Why Did This 22-Year-Old Entrepreneur Commit Suicide? |publisher=Gawker |first=Adrian |last=Chen |date=14 November 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111216130952/http://gawker.com/ilya-zhitomirskiy |archivedate=2011年12月16日 |accessdate=2016年2月5日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.smh.com.au/technology/technology-news/cofounder-of-facebook-alternative-diaspora-dead-at-22-20111115-1ng3i.html |title=Co-founder of Facebook alternative Diaspora dead at 22 |newspaper=Sydney Morning Herald |date=15 November 2011 |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2012-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120701023815/http://www.smh.com.au/technology/technology-news/cofounder-of-facebook-alternative-diaspora-dead-at-22-20111115-1ng3i.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://nymag.com/news/features/establishments/68512/ |title=Defacebook — Four young friends who are out to create a very different sort of social network |first=Emily |last=Nussbaum |newspaper=New York Magazine |date=September 26, 2010 |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2016-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127094537/http://nymag.com/news/features/establishments/68512/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年2月，合作创始人们听了由[[哥伦比亚法学院|哥伦比亚法学院]]教授，[[自由软件|自由软件]]活动人士[[伊本·莫格林|伊本·莫格林]]举办的演讲后，他们决定开始谋划Diaspora这一项目。
莫格林说，朱托米尔斯基是“极其聪明的”、“小组中最具理想主义的人”。莫格林说，当朱托米尔斯基面临选择毕业或选择参与此项目时，他选择了后者，因为他想要用他的时间做些促进人们自由的工作<ref name=NYTObit/>。

=== 死亡 ===
2011年11月12日夜，朱托米尔斯基被发现死在他在旧金山的家中。警察因怀疑其自杀向其打电话，却发现其已经自杀。<ref name="CNNMoney">{{Cite news|url = http://money.cnn.com/2011/11/14/technology/diaspora_cofounder_died/|title = Co-founder of social network Diaspora dies at 22|accessdate = 14 December 2011|last = Pepitone|first = Julianne|date = 14 November 2011|work = [[CNN|CNN]]|archive-date = 2016-01-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160122073353/http://money.cnn.com/2011/11/14/technology/diaspora_cofounder_died/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.webpronews.com/ilya-zhitomirskiy-update-reports-show-diaspora-co-founder-committed-suicide-2011-11 |title=Ilya Zhitomirskiy Update: Reports Show Diaspora Co-Founder Committed Suicide |publisher=WebProNews |first=Jeremy |last=Muncy |date=15 November 2011 |access-date=2016-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111213231432/http://www.webpronews.com/ilya-zhitomirskiy-update-reports-show-diaspora-co-founder-committed-suicide-2011-11 |archive-date=2011-12-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2012年8月，法医的尸检结果证明其是自杀身亡。他死于使用[[氦气|氦气]]进行的{{tsl|en|inert gas asphyxiation|稀有气体窒息}}。媒体曾报道朱托米尔斯基是因为Diaspora的开发而自杀的，但是Diaspora的另一合作创始人馬克士威·薩爾茨伯格（Maxwell Salzberg）不这样认为。薩爾茨伯格说：“没错，我同意作为一名创始人压力很大。但是这不是导致伊利亚死亡的原因。他有自己的问题。他生病了。”朱托米尔斯基的母亲恩娜未就其心理疾病史发表评论，但是她说：“我深信，倘若伊利亞没有开始这个项目而是留在学校，他会很好地活到现在。”<ref name="Weise10May12">{{cite news|url = http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2012-05-10/on-diasporas-social-network-you-own-your-data|title = On Diaspora's Social Network, You Own Your Data|accessdate = 14 May 2012|last = Weise|first = Karen|date = 15 May 2012|work = [[Bloomberg_Businessweek|Bloomberg Businessweek]]|archive-date = 2015-01-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150113012730/http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2012-05-10/on-diasporas-social-network-you-own-your-data|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Citation | url= http://tech.fortune.cnn.com/2013/03/26/ilya/ | title= Life, death, and free culture in the Mission | publisher= Fortune Magazine | first= Shaer | last= Matthew | date= 2013-03-26 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130331055234/http://tech.fortune.cnn.com/2013/03/26/ilya/ | archivedate= 2013-03-31 | accessdate= 2016-02-05 }}</ref>《{{Link-en|乡村之声|Village Voice}}》认为朱托米尔斯基“经常被评价为这个小组中最理想主义的和具有隐私意识的人”，并称其死亡为Diaspora的“毁灭性的挫折”。<ref name="Pinto15Feb12">{{Citation |url = http://www.villagevoice.com/2012-02-15/news/the-facebook-killers/3/ |title = Rise of the Facebook-Killers |page = 3 |accessdate = 20 February 2012 |last = Pinto |first = Nick |date = 15 February 2012 |newspaper = [[The_Village_Voice|The Village Voice]] |archive-date = 2012-02-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120219221613/http://www.villagevoice.com/2012-02-15/news/the-facebook-killers/3/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

